data.description: Beautiful newly built, 5/3 home on large corner lot with no back neighbors. Home features: Charming curb appeal, modern finishes, designer details, and much more! Gorgeous kitchen with island, tons of cabinet space, complete with walk-in pantry. Oversized indoor utility room! Open concept living space is perfect for entertaining along with the game/media room! Stunning master suite with sitting area and spa like bath retreat! Modern wood-look flooring throughout the main areas with neutral toned walls to fit any decor style.  Large backyard with covered patio, fully fenced, with plenty of room for a pool, play set, or for your fur baby to run around!  Sprinkler system to keep your yard hydrated all year long.   A/C and roof are less than three years old and roof is still under warranty.  Conveniently located close to I-45, Hardy Toll Road, and The Grand Parkway! Breckenridge Forest has wonderful amenities for residents!
